---
// Open Source section with GitHub link and getting started instructions
---

<section class="open-source-section" data-test="open-source-section" id="open-source">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Get Started with RootSpec</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      RootSpec is open source and ready to use. Start building better software
      with structured specifications today.
    </p>

    <div class="getting-started" data-test="getting-started">
      <h3>Quick Start</h3>
      <div class="code-block">
        <code>npx skills add rootspec/rootspec</code>
      </div>
      <p>Then run the four-command pipeline in any project directory:</p>
      <ol class="command-list">
        <li><code>/rs-init</code> - Set up project structure</li>
        <li><code>/rs-spec</code> - Create validated specification</li>
        <li><code>/rs-impl</code> - Generate working code</li>
        <li><code>/rs-validate</code> - Test implementation</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="resources">
      <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec" data-test="github-link" class="github-link">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
        </svg>
        View on GitHub
      </a>

      <div class="links-grid">
        <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec/blob/main/README.md" class="resource-link">
          Documentation
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec/tree/main/demos" class="resource-link">
          Examples
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec/issues" class="resource-link">
          Support
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .open-source-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: var(--bg-gray);
  }

  .open-source-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .getting-started {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .getting-started h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .code-block {
    background-color: var(--text-dark);
    color: var(--bg-light);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .command-list {
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 1.5rem auto;
  }

  .command-list li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
  }

  .resources {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .github-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background-color: var(--text-dark);
    color: var(--bg-light);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .github-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .links-grid {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .resource-link {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--primary-blue);
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .resource-link:hover {
    background-color: var(--primary-blue);
    color: white;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .open-source-section {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .open-source-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .code-block {
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 0.75rem;
    }

    .links-grid {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>